Check whethre eQTL effects have the same directions

Wei Sun

2023-01-06

Check the difference between the eGenes from Yazar et al.(2022) and eGenes identified by CSeQTL from GTEx whole blood RNA-seq data.

Setup

Load R libraries

library(data.table)
